codex
I’ve isolated a narrow gap: section parsing emits per-component slots, but it lacks explicit primary/terminal number/suffix roles, which weakens representation for section IDs like `190l`, `60e-3`, and `460bbb-5`. I’m adding those deterministic slots in both decompiler and triple generation, then extending the focused regression tests.
